  "Find the area between y = x^2 - 1 and y = x + 1.": "",
  "9/2": "",
  "6 (an integer)": "",
  "4 (a square)": "",
  "3 (an integer)": "",
  "Set x^2-1 = x+1: x^2-x-2 = 0, (x-2)(x+1) = 0, x = -1 and x = 2. On [-1,2], x+1 >= x^2-1. Area = integral from -1 to 2 of (x+1-(x^2-1)) dx = integral of (x+2-x^2) dx = [x^2/2+2x-x^3/3] from -1 to 2 = (2+4-8/3)-(1/2-2+1/3) = 10/3-(-7/6) = 10/3+7/6 = 27/6 = 9/2.": "",
  "Find the area between y = e^x and y = 1 from x = 0 to x = 1.": "",
  "e": "",
  "e - 1": "",
  "e - 2": "",
  "On [0,1], e^x >= 1. Area = integral from 0 to 1 of (e^x - 1) dx = [e^x - x] from 0 to 1 = (e-1)-(1-0) = e - 2.": "",
  "Find the area between y = x^3 and y = x from x = -1 to x = 1.": "",
  "On [-1,0]: x^3 >= x (both negative, x^3 is less negative). On [0,1]: x >= x^3. Area = integral from -1 to 0 of (x^3-x) dx + integral from 0 to 1 of (x-x^3) dx = [x^4/4-x^2/2] from -1 to 0 + [x^2/2-x^4/4] from 0 to 1 = (0-(1/4-1/2)) + (1/2-1/4) = 1/4 + 1/4 = 1/2.": "",
  "Find the area between x = y^2 and x = 4 (integrating with respect to y).": "",
  "y^2 = 4 at y = +/-2. Area = integral from -2 to 2 of (4 - y^2) dy = [4y - y^3/3] from -2 to 2 = (8-8/3)-(-8+8/3) = 32/3.": "",
  "Find the area between y = 2x and y = x^2 - 3.": "",
  "10": "",
  "Set 2x = x^2-3: x^2-2x-3 = 0, (x-3)(x+1) = 0. Intersection at x = -1, x = 3. Area = integral from -1 to 3 of (2x-(x^2-3)) dx = integral of (-x^2+2x+3) dx = [-x^3/3+x^2+3x] from -1 to 3 = (-9+9+9)-(1/3+1-3) = 9-(-5/3) = 9+5/3 = 32/3.": "",
